com.cyc.baseclient.subl

Class SubLResourceLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.subl.SubLResourceLoader

  • public class SubLResourceLoader
extends Object
    This class is designed to check a Cyc server for a set of SubL source files and load any which are missing from it.

      • loadMissingResources

        public List<SubLSourceFile> loadMissingResources(List<SubLSourceFile> resources)
                                          throws CycApiException,
                                                 CycConnectionException
        For a list of SubLSourceFiles, load any which are missing from the Cyc server. Note that this function will evaluate the SubLSourceFiles in the order in which they appear in the List argument.
        Parameters:
        resources - the ordered list of resources to load, if missing.
        Returns:
        a list of the SubLSourceFiles which were loaded by the method.
        Throws:
        CycApiException
        CycConnectionException
